James de Villiers, News24 (File, News24) Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories Johannesburg &ndash; A body of a man was found in a dam at Monte Casino on Wednesday morning.&nbsp;Monte Casino spokesperson Priya Naidoo said a staff member discovered the body and immediately notified police.&nbsp;Douglasdale police station spokesperson Mpho Kgasoane told News24 that the body was found in a decomposed state.&nbsp; Kgasoane said police had no leads about the cause of death.&nbsp; "We appeal to the public to come forward with any information that might assist with the case," she said.&nbsp; 24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.